## THIS IS A SMART CONTRACT THAT CAN BE USED FOR A BIKESHARING PURPOSE
## USERS CAN BUY TOKENS FROM THE CONTRACT AND RENT A BIKE BUT ONE WILL HAVE TO PUT
## 3 TIMES THE AMOUNT THATS 15000 TOKENS ONCE A USER RENTS THE 15000 REQUIRED TOKENS WILL BE BURNED
## WHEN THE USER RETURNS THE BIKE THE TOKENS WILL BE MINTED BACK TO THE USER

## NOTE I HAVE TESTED THE CODE BUT NO ASSURANCES THAT YOU WONT ENCOUNTER A BUG OF SOME SORT 

